*easyXDM-tester*

This is a simple text chat demo snippet Im hoping you'll find useful. Keep in mind the hackers over at easyxdm.net have quite a few more elaborate demos to punch around. 

There is no reason not to add encryption, real nick provisioning, etc.

Go ahead and read up. Happy Coding. :)

Changelog
==========
v0.01
- simple text chat application with easyXDM (working)
